DIBS Application: ebcdic->txt


Build Instructions:

Navigate to the src directory and run command:
make


Execution Instructions:

The name of the application binary is:
conv

This code takes the following inputs from the command line:
    -i input file
    -o output file
    -a (optional) convert from txt to ebcdic (defaults ebcdic to txt)
    -n (optional) specify number of runs (defaults to 1)

To execute the binary, run the command in the form::
./conv [-i inputfile] [-o outputfile] [-a] [-n]
